articles.title: Ono Ramen: Owner of Kulon achieves lifelong goal of opening ramen shop
articles.content: The rise of fusion restaurants is nothing short of remarkable. Founder and owner Haris always loved food, which he credits to his vibrant home of Indonesia. In 2018, Haris decided to open a food stall called IndoJava in the canteen of Singapore Polytechnic. Serving authentic Indonesian food, Haris quickly received positive responses. articles.title: $52k lost to scammers impersonating MHA officers since September
